OL,3,CWhat is Plaid Cymru pledging for Wales
OL,4,Cin its manifesto?
OL,6,F"For Fairness, For Ambition, For
OL,7,FWales" reads the cover of Plaid
OL,8,FCymru's green manifesto booklet.
OL,10,FInside is a pledge to demand "fair
OL,11,Ffunding" for Wales from Westminster.
OL,13,FIts leader, Rhun ap Iorwerth, says 14
OL,14,Fyears of Tory cuts and "weak
OL,15,Fopposition" from Labour means only
OL,16,FPlaid Cymru offers a "real
OL,17,Falternative" in Wales.
