OL,3,CWhat is Plaid Cymru pledging for Wales
OL,4,Cin its manifesto?
OL,6,FITV News Wales Reporter Rhys Williams
OL,7,Fexplains what Plaid Cymru is proposing
OL,8,Fto offer voters after launching its
OL,9,FGeneral Election manifesto
OL,11,FThe manifesto contains six headline
OL,12,Fpledges:
OL,14,F1. Secure the #4bn owed to Wales from
OL,15,FHS2 to invest in improving public
OL,16,Ftransport infrastructure and reverse
OL,17,Flocal bus cuts.
OL,19,F2. Demand a fair funding system for
OL,20,FWales, "based around our needs, giving
OL,21,Fus the public services we deserve."
