OL,3,CWhat is Plaid Cymru pledging for Wales
OL,4,Cin its manifesto?
OL,6,FThis is clearly a primarily economic
OL,7,Fpitch to Welsh voters from Plaid
OL,8,FCymru. Many of the promises are based
OL,9,Fon the scrapping of the Barnett
OL,10,FFormula - the system by which money is
OL,11,Fallocated to governments in Cardiff,
OL,12,FEdinburgh and Belfast.
OL,14,FMr ap Iorwerth told journalists his
OL,15,Fparty is the only one advocating for
OL,16,Fthe abolition of the formula in favour
OL,17,Fof a "needs-based model."
OL,19,FOn a similar theme, Plaid Cymru is
OL,20,Fpledging to secure the #4bn it says is
OL,21,Fowed to Wales from the building of HS2.
