OL,3,CWhat is Plaid Cymru pledging for Wales
OL,4,Cin its manifesto?
OL,6,FThis is because the UK government
OL,7,Fclassified the London to Birmingham
OL,8,Fline as an "England and Wales"
OL,9,Fproject, rather than an "England only"
OL,10,Fproject.
OL,12,FWere Wales to be treated in line with
OL,13,Fboth Scotland and Northern Ireland
OL,14,Fthrough the Barnett Formula on HS2
OL,15,Ffunding, Wales would receive #3.9bn in
OL,16,Fconsequential cash.
OL,18,FThis is a call also made by both the
OL,19,FWelsh Conservatives and Welsh Labour,
OL,20,Fbut the UK Government has rejected the
OL,21,Fdemand.
