OL,3,CWhat is Plaid Cymru pledging for Wales
OL,4,Cin its manifesto?
OL,6,FBoth Labour leader Sir Keir Starmer
OL,7,Fand Shadow Chancellor Rachel Reeves
OL,8,Fhave refused to commit to releasing
OL,9,Fthe cash to Cardiff.
OL,11,FThe party promises to prepare a Green
OL,12,FPaper on the path to independence, but
OL,13,Fit takes 42 pages of the manifesto
OL,14,Fbefore the subject is mentioned in any
OL,15,Fdetail.
OL,17,FThat decision perhaps comes as no
OL,18,Fsurprise when a recent poll showed
OL,19,Findependence was only the 15th most
OL,20,Fimportant subject mentioned by Welsh
OL,21,Fvoters.
